# NomaanOS

Personal project: NomaanOS â€” phone-first, Termux-driven personal OS environment.

## Goals
- Secure, reproducible Termux + proot environment
- Git-backed configs and scripts
- Automated backups (GitHub + Google Drive)
- Modular project folders: src, scripts, bin, docs

## Quick start (local)
- Work inside `~/workspace/nomaanos`
- Scripts in `scripts/`, executables in `bin/`
